# Long-Term Vision

In a future containing billions of autonomous systems, trust changes must propagate globally in near real time.

An agent that becomes compromised in one organization should become untrusted across the ecosystem within minutes rather than weeks.

Revocation is therefore not a supporting feature.

It is a foundational requirement of the agent internet.

---

# Conclusion

Agent Revocation & Trust Distribution provides the mechanisms required to remove trust safely, transparently, and efficiently across the APP ecosystem and serves as a critical component of secure autonomous infrastructure.
